28 February 2011The Minister of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries, Ms Tina Joemat-Pettersson, will brief the media on the possible outbreak of Foot and Mouth Disease.The briefing will be held as follows:Date: Monday, 28 February 2011 Time: 13h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre 120 Plein Street, Parliament NOTE: There will be a link-up to Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaRSVP: Professor Ndawonde (Pretoria) Cell: 078 456 5738 Sbongile Dalasile (Cape Town) Cell: 071 292 1006Media enquires: Selby BokabaCell: 082 778 0245Issued by: Government Communication and Information System